item.title: Project 2
item.description: This dataset of 75 observations contains information to study any potential correlations or predictors of relationships between salary, educational background degree type, etc. There are many factors that influence salaries and degrees obtained such as experience, opportunity, family operations, business owner status, future goals, etc., but comparisons between this smaller set of variables may provide some type of trend and clarity on the relationships.
